name: Internship King
overview:
The world’s best internship community.

InternshipKing offers internship reviews, internship postings, and internship advice. Our goal is to celebrate internship programs and provide students the best internship resource in the world. We also want to promote and recognize world-class internship programs. We believe that internships are great ways to find student talent and allow students the chance to gain experience in a certain field.

Furthermore, we want to be the premier location for advice and news. When internship news breaks, our goal is to be there first. We also want to provide student resources for internship interviews, internship cover letters, internship resumes, and internship search tips.
